    Z "Ahora tengo curiosidad."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:833
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_7e936a82:

    # "Getting anything beyond the most basic words out of Fairy seems an inpossible task."
    "Sacarle algo más que las palabras más básicas a Fairy parece una tarea imposible."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:834
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_8e87b562:

    # "Whatever, whoever she was in the past, that woman is gone, now only Fairy remains, a mindless sex craving and sex dependent toy. She will be of service that way, but nothing more."
    "Fuera quien fuera en el pasado, esa mujer ha desaparecido; ahora solo queda Fairy, un juguete sin cerebro dependiente del sexo y adicto a él. Servirá para eso, pero para nada más."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:837
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:838
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_6091e0a8:

    # "You hear the door open and look up..."
    "Oyes abrirse la puerta y miras hacia arriba..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:841
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_9ee7a251:

    # W "Get a move on, come now. You're not an animal... or are you?"
    W "Muévete, vamos. No eres un animal... ¿o sí?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:842
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_91d9cfed:

