    W "¡Ey, no tires de la cadena!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:846
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_74822589:

    # "You see [W] tighten her grip on the chain tied to Fairy's new collar..."
    "Ves que [W] aprieta con fuerza la cadena atada al nuevo collar de Fairy..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:849
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_a802be4a:

    # W "Poor girl, you've had your chance. Don't worry though. You will be well fed and groomed... but we will do things with you... I can already picture some of them.."
    W "Pobre chica, ya tuviste tu oportunidad. Pero no te preocupes, estarás bien alimentada y aseada... pero vamos a divertirnos un poco contigo... Ya me estoy imaginando unas cuantas cosas..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:852
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_697832cc:

    # "As you wife stares down at Fairy, you acknowledge the truth in her words."
    "Mientras tu mujer mira fijamente a Fairy, reconoces la verdad de sus palabras."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:853
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_825f4f00:

    # "As you look at your wife, you see her fierce expression. She is in her element, in command of the little redhead."
    "Al mirar a tu esposa, ves su expresión feroz. Está en su elemento, dominando por completo a la pequeña pelirroja."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:854
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_5c9333bf:

    # "You have had toys of this nature before, however briefly."
    "Has tenido juguetes de esta naturaleza antes, aunque brevemente."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:855
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_8f2f6ba2:

    # "It always amazes you to see your faithful and devoted wife take control of someone. The casual observer who knows her on the surface would not see it."
    "Siempre te asombra ver a tu fiel y abnegada esposa tomar el control de alguien. Un observador casual que solo la conozca por encima jamás lo vería."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:856
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_605fa675:

    # "But you know this side of her, that lurks under the surface of your otherwise submissive wife, like a lioness waiting to pounce."
    "But tú conoces ese lado suyo que acecha bajo la superficie de tu por lo demás sumisa esposa, como una leona esperando para abalanzarse."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:857
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_a60c6747:

    # "Her entire body language seems to change subtly, and it's never for too long, but it something that has always impressed you."
    "Todo su lenguaje corporal parece cambiar sutilmente, y nunca es por mucho tiempo, pero es algo que siempre te ha impresionado."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:860
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_08421f0f:

    # "Your wife drags Fairy into the room, towering over her. On all fours and dragging her legs across the floor, Fairy doesn't say a word, obedient like a hungry dog..."
    "Tu mujer arrastra a Fairy a la habitación, sobresaliendo por encima de ella. A cuatro patas y arrastrando las piernas por el suelo, Fairy no dice una palabra, obediente como un perro hambriento..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:863
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_6ce89e9b:

    # "The girl whimpers, as you look at her naked frail form."
    "La chica gime, mientras observas su frágil forma desnuda."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:866
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_78b6412e:

    # "Chained to the bench you're sitting on, the girl assumes a position that she has obviously been trained into before, one of servitude and attendance."
    "Encadenada al banco en el que estás sentado, la chica asume una posición en la que obviamente ha sido entrenada antes, una de servidumbre y asistencia."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:867
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_8b0dd42d:

    # "You look at her pretty face and stare into her green eyes, looking for a glimpse of something, fear, hurt, anger or even resignation..."
    "Miras su bonita cara y clavas la mirada en sus ojos verdes, buscando un atisbo de algo, miedo, dolor, rabia o incluso resignación..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:868
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_227303cb:

    # "Instead you find nothing. Just a passive presence, barely aware of her surroundings but still ready to jump at the first threat, or to serve, at the first command."
    "En cambio, no encuentra nada. Solo una presencia pasiva, apenas consciente de lo que la rodea pero lista para reaccionar ante cualquier amenaza o para servir a la primera orden."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:871
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_cbf29b57:

    # "Now that she has relinquished the power that comes with holding the leash, [W] is smiling at you, her usual self again..."
    "Ahora que ha soltado el poder que da llevar la correa, [W] te sonríe, volviendo a ser la de siempre..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:872
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_885cda2a:

    # "To the point that you wonder if your perception of her was maybe altered by your mutual devotion. Then you remember the many occasions in which your lioness showed her claws."
    "Hasta el punto de que te preguntas si tu percepción de ella quizá se vio alterada por vuestra devoción mutua. Entonces recuerdas las muchas ocasiones en las que tu leona enseñó las garras."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:875
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_cc77cc9e:

    # W "Well, here she is. As pretty and exotic as I've ever seen anybody, but... she might as well not be here at all."
    W "Bueno, aquí la tienes. Es de las tías más guapas y exóticas que he visto en mi vida, pero... como si no estuviera."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:876
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_7bea13dd:

    # W "Just a body for you.. for us, to use as we please. It's a pity that these thing should happen but... what can you do?"
    W "Solo un cuerpo para ti... para nosotros, para usarlo como nos dé la gana. Es una pena que pasen estas cosas, pero... ¿qué se le va a hacer?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:879
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_a0935498:

    # Z "We tried. We honestly did our best to bring her back from wherever her mind has decided to hide."
    Z "Lo intentamos. Sinceramente, hicimos todo lo posible para traerla de vuelta de dondequiera que su mente haya decidido esconderse."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:880
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_25195aaa:

    # Z "If there's nothing to be done for her, we might as well make use of her to suit our wants."
    Z "Si no hay nada que hacer por ella, podríamos utilizarla para satisfacer nuestros deseos."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:883
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_a0251137:

    # "Indifferent, or maybe unaware, Fairy sits there staring into nowhere, letting the words wash over her."
    "Indiferente, o tal vez inconsciente, Fairy permanece sentada mirando a la nada, dejando que las palabras la inunden."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:888
translate spanish fairy_broken_outcome_09d1b5fd:

