    "Algún tiempo después, vuelves a la celda llevando un viejo somier y un colchón..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1454
translate spanish fairy_bed_7f050f3c:

    # "You leave the cell again, coming back with an armful of linen."
    "Vuelves a salir de la celda y regresas con un cargamento de sábanas."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1457
translate spanish fairy_bed_22dddf8c:

    # "After a bit of work manoeuvering the frame into the cell, you look at the result of your efforts."
    "Después de un rato de trabajo maniobrando el armazón para introducirlo en la celda, miras el resultado de tus esfuerzos."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1458
translate spanish fairy_bed_2fecb5f0:

    # Z "This should do for now."
    Z "Esto debería servir por ahora."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1462
translate spanish fairy_bed_41e6c879:

    # Z "Emilia washed the sheets. They're clean. The mattress was in storage, but is still soft."
    Z "Emilia ha lavado las sábanas. Están limpias. El colchón estaba guardado, pero aún está blando."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1464
translate spanish fairy_bed_8f8cf030:

    # Z "My wife cleaned the sheets. This is a good mattress, from [A]'s old bed."
    Z "Mi esposa limpió las sábanas. Este es un buen colchón, de la vieja cama de [A]."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1467
translate spanish fairy_bed_7d31e4b6:

    # Z "You will be a lot more comfortable than on the bench or the floor."
    Z "Estarás mucho más cómoda que en el banco o en el suelo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1468
translate spanish fairy_bed_e2097019:

    # Z "Go on then... Try it."
    Z "Pues adelante... Inténtalo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1471
translate spanish fairy_bed_ba5d430a:

    # "She hesitantly approaches the bed. You wonder when, if ever, she slept in a normal bed?"
    "Ella se acerca vacilante a la cama. Te preguntas cuándo, si es que alguna vez ha dormido en una cama normal."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1472
translate spanish fairy_bed_ea29de98:

    # "Maybe you will find out eventually."
    "Tal vez lo descubras más adelante."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1475
translate spanish fairy_bed_e7913b4a:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1476
translate spanish fairy_bed_fbd8d5c9:

    # "Seeing how she still hesitates, you understand that you will have to guide her every step of the way."
    "Al ver que sigue dudando, comprendes que tendrás que guiarla en cada paso del camino."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1479
translate spanish fairy_bed_3610cd89:

    # Z "Come on, touch it."
    Z "Vamos, tócala."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1488
translate spanish fairy_bed_1e165efb:

    # F "...!"
    F "¡...!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1494
translate spanish fairy_bed_6a8c49e9:

    # "She touches the fabric, and looks at it in surprise."
    "Ella toca la tela, y la mira sorprendida."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1495
translate spanish fairy_bed_9135b006:

    # "You wonder what she might be thinking, as she becomes less skittish, nervous, and settles with a calm expression."
    "Te preguntas qué estará pensando, ya que se vuelve menos asustadiza y nerviosa, y se instala en una expresión tranquila."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1496
translate spanish fairy_bed_d6fa4b97:

    # Z "Try it. Go on, lay down..."
    Z "Inténtalo. Vamos, túmbate..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1499
translate spanish fairy_bed_74dd25dd:

    # F "Lay...?"
    F "¿Túmbarme...?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1500
translate spanish fairy_bed_7dee9bb8:

    # Z "Yes...."
    Z "Sí..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1501
translate spanish fairy_bed_acbfda2e:

    # "With a measured movement, without actually touching her, you gesture towards the bed."
    "Con un movimiento medido, sin llegar a tocarla, haces un gesto hacia la cama."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1504
translate spanish fairy_bed_49776032:

    # "She lays down, her eyes still darting around like those of hunted prey."
    "Ella se tumba, con los ojos todavía desorbitados como los de una presa acorralada."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1505
translate spanish fairy_bed_2ee57576:

    # "Her breathing is nervous and you look at this frail figure shivering a little as she tries for a comfortable position."
    "Su respiración es acelerada y miras a esta frágil figura temblar un poco mientras intenta una posición cómoda."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1508
translate spanish fairy_bed_4fb162f4:

    # "Instinctively she goes into fetal position, her body finally relaxing a little."
    "Instintivamente se pone en posición fetal, su cuerpo por fin se relaja un poco."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1509
translate spanish fairy_bed_c0712375:

    # "You notice the bruises on her skin seem to be slowly healing."
    "Notas que los moratones de su piel parecen curarse lentamente."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1512
translate spanish fairy_bed_c0795027:

    # "She looks up at you from there, hesitantly, a tentative hint of a smile coursing her lips."
    "Te mira desde allí, vacilante, con una tímida sonrisa en los labios."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1515
translate spanish fairy_bed_bf61d0ee:

    # "As you look at her, her natural exotic beauty strikes you again."
    "Al mirarla, su exótica belleza natural vuelve a impresionarte."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1516
translate spanish fairy_bed_c8306e84:

    # "Between her freckled skin, her piercing eyes and red curls, you can't help but being attracted to her."
    "Entre su piel pecosa, sus ojos penetrantes y sus rizos pelirrojos, no puedes evitar sentirte atraído por ella."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1519
translate spanish fairy_bed_7dcb841b:

    # "You notice she laid down on top of her sheets, maybe out of a habit of immediate obedience."
    "Te das cuenta de que se ha tumbado encima de las sábanas, tal vez por costumbre de obediencia inmediata."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1520
translate spanish fairy_bed_eaeb9d3a:

    # "The thought occurs to you that she might not be used to even seeing proper bed linen, so she just did what she was told."
    "Se te ocurre pensar que tal vez no esté acostumbrada ni siquiera a ver ropa de cama adecuada, así que se limitó a hacer lo que le dijeron."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1523
translate spanish fairy_bed_9d292093:

    # "With some manoeuvring, you manage to pull the sheets from under her, and tuck her in, the patterned blanket covering her slim figure."
    "Con algunas maniobras, consigues sacar las sábanas de debajo de ella y arroparla, con la manta estampada cubriendo su esbelta figura."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1524
translate spanish fairy_bed_ca3d186a:

    # "As you were pulling at the blankets, you noticed Fairy being as still as she possibly could, which actually made your task more bothersome."
    "Mientras tirabas de las mantas, te diste cuenta de que Fairy estaba lo más quieta posible, lo que en realidad hizo que tu tarea fuera más engorrosa."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1527
translate spanish fairy_bed_8df925cc:

    # "Immediately she closes her eyes, but you can tell she's doing what she thinks is expected of her.. so you stick around for a little while."
    "Inmediatamente cierra los ojos, pero te das cuenta de que está haciendo lo que cree que se espera de ella... así que te quedas un rato."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1528
translate spanish fairy_bed_e6da932c:

    # "For several minutes, she keeps her eyes shut, trying to move as little as possible. Only the slight movement of her chest betrays her, as she breathes as quietly as she can manage."
    "Durante varios minutos, mantiene los ojos cerrados, intentando moverse lo menos posible. Sólo el leve movimiento de su pecho la delata, mientras respira tan silenciosamente como puede."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1531
translate spanish fairy_bed_e214607a:

    # "Eventually, exhaustion overcomes Fairy and beats her nervous energy, as she drifts into the deepest of sleeps."
    "Finalmente, el cansancio vence a Fairy y anula su energía nerviosa, mientras cae en el más profundo de los sueños."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1532
translate spanish fairy_bed_586b2128:

    # "Before your eyes, you see her features soften, her jaw unclench, her limbs sink deeper into the mattress as tension abandons them."
    "Ante tus ojos, ves cómo sus facciones se suavizan, su mandíbula se relaja, sus miembros se hunden más en el colchón a medida que la tensión los abandona."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1535
translate spanish fairy_bed_8b319073:

    # "You walk to the door of the cell and look back at the girl, now seemingly at peace with the world."
    "Te acercas a la puerta de la celda y vuelves a mirar a la chica, ahora aparentemente en paz con el mundo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1536
translate spanish fairy_bed_e0ebd51f:

    # "You take the torch with you and leave her in darkness."
    "Te llevas la antorcha contigo y la dejas en la oscuridad."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1542
translate spanish fairy_bed_b98c9d83:

    # Z "I will arrange proper bedding for you."
    Z "Arreglaré ropa de cama adecuada para ti."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1543
translate spanish fairy_bed_20b0d6b3:

    # Z "Wait for me."
    Z "Espérame."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1546
translate spanish fairy_bed_c3be07dd:

    # "Eventually,you come back into the room and place a small but soft square mattress on the floor..."
    "Finalmente, vuelves a la habitación y colocas un pequeño pero blando colchón cuadrado en el suelo..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1549
translate spanish fairy_bed_e35fe5dc:

    # Z "You will sleep better on this instead of the bench."
    Z "Dormirás mejor sobre esto que sobre el banco."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1550
translate spanish fairy_bed_23b0ebe5:

    # Z "I have no use for a slave covered in bruises, so... don't let me catch you hiding under the bench again. Use this."
    Z "No me sirve de nada una esclava cubierta de moratones, así que... no dejes que vuelva a pillarte escondida bajo el banco. Usa esto."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1551
translate spanish fairy_bed_e7913b4a_1:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1552
translate spanish fairy_bed_fff07f53:

    # Z "Come on, try it out."
    Z "Vamos, pruébala."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1555
translate spanish fairy_bed_c048744b:

    # "She kneels down and curiously looks at it..."
    "Se arrodilla y lo mira con curiosidad..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1556
translate spanish fairy_bed_e7913b4a_2:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1559
translate spanish fairy_bed_15262910:

    # Z "Lay down. I want to see if it's big enough."
    Z "Acuéstate. Quiero ver si es lo suficientemente grande."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1562
translate spanish fairy_bed_b55a9b27:

    # "She does as you say, assuming a fetal position..."
    "Hace lo que dices, asumiendo una posición fetal..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1563
translate spanish fairy_bed_40633590:

    # "Curling up into a ball, you see a slight tremor in her knees."
    "Haciéndose un ovillo, ves un ligero temblor en sus rodillas."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1564
translate spanish fairy_bed_8b73f144:

    # "It's hard to say if she's still afraid or maybe cold."
    "Es difícil decir si todavía tiene miedo o tal vez frío."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1567
translate spanish fairy_bed_2e3cc5d1:

    # Z "There you go. Now sleep. Tomorrow is another day."
    Z "Ya está. Ahora a dormir. Mañana será otro día."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1571
translate spanish fairy_bed_371b2e82:

    # Z "You've come a long way, but the day has been long. You need some rest."
    Z "Has recorrido un largo camino, pero el día ha sido largo. Necesitas descansar."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1573
translate spanish fairy_bed_f77d2009:

    # Z "You've come a long way, girl. You deserve to rest for now."
    Z "Has recorrido un largo camino, chica. Te mereces descansar por ahora."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1574
translate spanish fairy_bed_693b6942:

    # Z "Good night."
    Z "Buenas noches."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1577
translate spanish fairy_bed_e7913b4a_3:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1580
translate spanish fairy_bed_b3f672f1:

    # "You extinguish the torch..."
    "Apagas la antorcha..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1583
translate spanish fairy_bed_398ab5e9:

    # "You can hear her soft breathing getting deeper as sleep embraces her. This is probably the most comfortable she's been in a long while."
    "Puedes oír su suave respiración, cada vez más profunda, mientras el sueño la abraza. Esto es probablemente lo más cómoda que ha estado en mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1584
translate spanish fairy_bed_cb6a49b7:

    # "It may not be the best you can give her, but for now this will do, you think to yourself."
    "Puede que no sea lo mejor que puedas darle, pero por ahora esto servirá, piensas para ti."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1591
translate spanish fairy_bath_f6e95c1a:

    # Z "You've been in here for some time now."
    Z "Llevas aquí ya algún tiempo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1592
translate spanish fairy_bath_617dee55:

    # Z "You're dirty, and that just will not do."
    Z "Estás sucia, y eso no puede ser."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1594
translate spanish fairy_bath_fb8014db:

    # Z "Don't get nervous. I need my slaves to be clean."
    Z "No te pongas nerviosa. Necesito que mis esclavos estén limpios."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1596
translate spanish fairy_bath_d68c0400:

    # Z "Don't worry now, you will be safe."
    Z "Ahora no te preocupes, estarás a salvo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1599
translate spanish fairy_bath_ea3294f6:

    # Z "My maid will take care of you."
    Z "Mi criada se ocupará de ti."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1600
translate spanish fairy_bath_c74d9ff2:

    # Z "She's a very well trained slave. You will learn much from her."
    Z "Ella es una esclava muy bien preparada. Aprenderás mucho de ella."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1602
translate spanish fairy_bath_9b20529d:

    # Z "Emilia will take care of you."
    Z "Emilia cuidará de ti."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1603
translate spanish fairy_bath_13bd343c:

    # Z "She's the maid in this house. You should listen to her, she can teach you many things."
    Z "Es la criada de esta casa. Deberías escucharla, ella te podrá enseñar muchas cosas."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1605
translate spanish fairy_bath_9c04a28f:

    # Z "I will take care of you myself."
    Z "Yo mismo me ocuparé de ti."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1606
translate spanish fairy_bath_166f85aa:

    # Z "Understood?"
    Z "¿Entendido?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1609
translate spanish fairy_bath_3af08117:

    # F "Yes, Master."
    F "Sí, Amo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1615
translate spanish fairy_bath_f1e9b688:

    # "A few minutes later..."
    "Unos minutos más tarde..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1619
translate spanish fairy_bath_c8cc79e1:

    # "As you get into the bathroom, the sun is piercing through the curtained windows. You see Emilia heating up pails of water."
    "Al entrar en el cuarto de baño, el sol atraviesa las ventanas con cortinas. Ves a Emilia calentando cubos de agua."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1620
translate spanish fairy_bath_1d328116:

    # "Fairy seems to be sitting idly, staring curiously at your maid."
    "Fairy parece estar sentada sin hacer nada, mirando con curiosidad a tu criada."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1623
translate spanish fairy_bath_64ffee13:

    # E "No need to be nervous. It is almost ready and then we can begin."
    E "No te pongas nerviosa. Ya está casi listo y podremos empezar."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1627
translate spanish fairy_bath_b46059e2:

    # "She dunks the sponge in the water..."
    "Moja la esponja en el agua..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1630
translate spanish fairy_bath_7204ec75:

    # "You head inside the room and lean on a nearby closet..."
    "Entras en la habitación y te apoyas en un armario cercano..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1631
translate spanish fairy_bath_2f6cc7e3:

    # E "Oh, hello, Master. I didn't notice you come in."
    E "Oh, hola, Amo. No me di cuenta de que entraste."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1632
translate spanish fairy_bath_49be3960:

    # Z "It's fine. Focus on what you're doing."
    Z "Está bien. Concéntrate en lo que estás haciendo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1635
translate spanish fairy_bath_976ed438:

    # "She moves over to Fairy, and begins washing her..."
    "Se acerca a Fairy y empieza a lavarla..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1639
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_669c4fa3:

    # E "Hold still. This is good for you."
    E "No te muevas. Esto es bueno para ti."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1640
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_e85994ce:

    # "In her caring fashion, she cushion's Fairy's head with her own cleavage, while caressing her cheeks and slowly starting to wash her..."
    "A su manera cariñosa, amortigua la cabeza de Fairy con su propio pecho, mientras acaricia sus mejillas y empieza a lavarla lentamente...."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1641
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_8650d507:

    # E "You have so much dirt caked on your skin... I guess you haven't had a proper bath in a long time."
    E "Tienes mucha suciedad acumulada en la piel... Supongo que hace mucho que no te bañas como es debido."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1644
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_f223cc5b:

    # E "It's okay. You can calm down, now."
    E "No pasa nada. Ahora puedes relajarte."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1645
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_b4e7a587:

    # "Emilia continues to use her most soothing tones, to placate Fairy..."
    "Emilia sigue usando sus tonos más tranquilizadores, para aplacar a Fairy..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1648
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_e7913b4a:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1649
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_1620d587:

    # E "I am just giving you a good wash. You will feel better for it, I promise."
    E "Sólo te estoy dando un buen lavado. Te sentirás mejor por ello, te lo prometo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1652
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_e7913b4a_1:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1653
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_7f9cbea0:

    # E "There, there."
    E "Ahí, ahí."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1656
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_9321d116:

    # "For a moment, Emilia drops the sponge, and starts to gently caress Fairy's still tense chest in something of a sensual but comforting hug."
    "Por un momento, Emilia deja caer la esponja y comienza a acariciar suavemente el pecho aún tenso de Fairy en una especie de abrazo sensual pero reconfortante."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1659
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_2b8b8b98:

    # "Seeing this play out, you see Fairy's long legs stop trembling, and slowly submerge into the water."
    "Al ver esto, ves como las largas piernas de Fairy dejan de temblar, y se sumergen lentamente en el agua."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1660
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_c1e5cf7c:

    # "She seems to enjoy the experience. You wonder when the last time was that she had a proper bath, if ever, as you realise that for most people, even in Zeta, using water this way is a luxury."
    "Parece disfrutar de la experiencia. Te preguntas cuándo fue la última vez que se bñó en condiciones, si es que lo hizo alguna vez, ya que te das cuenta de que para la mayoría de la gente, incluso en Zeta, utilizar el agua de esta manera es un lujo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1663
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_7329681e:

    # E "..."
    E "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1666
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_99f1e285:

    # "You take a step back, not saying anything."
    "Das un paso atrás, sin decir nada."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1669
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_d615e4fa:

    # "She starts humming a song..."
    "Ella empieza a tararear una canción..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1670
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_f9c200a9:

    # E "Å mang en tår på m1 kinn ha runne, eg tenkte vetet det hadde sprange..."
    E "Å mang en tår på m1 kinn ha runne, eg tenkte vetet det hadde sprange..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1673
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_c6b33d0d:

    # E "Å eg har gráte så mang ei tar, som det er dagar I tusind år..."
    E "Å eg har gráte så mang ei tar, som det er dagar I tusind år..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1676
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_2267b368:

    # E "You seem worried..."
    E "Pareces preocupada..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1678
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_c4616e3b:

    # E "...but you don't need to be worried here."
    E "... pero aquí no tienes por qué preocuparte."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1679
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_b6032fdf:

    # E "Our Master will be kind to you, I'm sure."
    E "Nuestro Amo será amable contigo, estoy segura."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1680
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_74c7b49a:

    # E "We will have a good life here, together."
    E "Aquí tendremos una buena vida, todos juntos."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1683
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_e7913b4a_2:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1684
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_96d9cf29:

    # "You notice how she seems to be emotionally affected by what Emilia said to her."
    "Te das cuenta de cómo ella parece estar afectada emocionalmente por lo que Emilia le dijo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1685
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_a37c67bc:

    # "Maybe it was also because of her angelic voice?"
    "¿Quizá también se debía a su voz angelical?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1687
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_c4616e3b_1:

    # E "...but you don't need to be worried here."
    E "... pero aquí no tienes por qué preocuparte."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1688
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_c62af26e:

    # E "Serve our Master well, and he will give you a good life, like he gives me."
    E "Sirve bien a nuestro Amo, y él te dará una buena vida, como me la da a mí."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1689
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_5228a152:

    # E "Maybe we will serve Master together, soon?"
    E "¿Tal vez pronto sirvamos juntas al Amo?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1692
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_e7913b4a_3:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:1693
translate spanish re_fairy_bath_d7107740:

