    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2347
translate spanish bf129_62086e11:

    # Zt "Such a nice body. Perfect shape, slim but toned."
    Zt "Qué buen cuerpo tiene. Una silueta perfecta, delgada pero tonificada."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2348
translate spanish bf129_98a6ffa8:

    # Zt "She seems young, must be barely in her twenties."
    Zt "Parece joven, a duras penas andará por los veinte."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2350
translate spanish bf129_768652cb:

    # Zt "I see no scars either. I wonder what happened before they decided to put her in that cage."
    Zt "Tampoco veo cicatrices. Me pregunto qué pasó antes de que decidieran meterla en esa jaula."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2352
translate spanish bf129_39956a28:

    # Zt "[Ki] and [Ko] must've not realized this, otherwise they would've sold her off quickly."
    Zt "[Ki] y [Ko] no debieron darse cuenta de esto, si no, la habrían vendido rápido."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2353
translate spanish bf129_52e9004a:

    # Zt "I know those greedy bastards..."
    Zt "Conozco a esos codiciosos bastardos..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2356
