    Z "Seguro que son unas bonitas caderas."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2412
translate spanish bf129_f89697e1:

    # Zt "The decayed hold slaves, but I am not sure if she is the result of selective breeding. It can't be."
    Zt "Los Decaídos tienen esclavos, pero dudo que ella sea el fruto de una cría selectiva. Es imposible."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2414
translate spanish bf129_dcb8e0b3:

    # Zt "They didn't seem to use her as what they call \"cattle\" either way."
    Zt "De todos modos, no parece que la utilicen como lo que llaman \"ganado\"."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2416
translate spanish bf129_213ae663:

    # Zt "Looking at how [Ki] and [Ko] treated her, it seems unlikely she was used for anything other than personal relief."
    Zt "Viendo cómo la trataron [Ki] y [Ko], parece poco probable que la utilizaran para algo más que para su alivio personal."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2417
translate spanish bf129_c7fe5e99:

